These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, cat, hamster, snake, rat
There are 7 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, spanish, french, turkish, thai, australian
7 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, snooker, billiard, bridge, poker, chess
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, subway, taxi, train, tram, van
 1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 2. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the turkish is the person driving the tram##1
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person driving the boat is the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the owner of the snake##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 9. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
10. the australian is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
11. the thai is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
13. the turkish is on the right of the brazilian##1
14. the person playing canasta is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
15. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the mexican and the person driving the train##2
16. the thai is on the left of the spanish##1
17. the owner of the cat is the person driving the train##1
18. the french is on the far left or far right##3
19. the thai is on the left or right of the mexican##3
20. the thai is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
21. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
22. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
23. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the mexican##3
24. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
25. the turkish is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
26. the owner of the goat is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Pet        | goat | snake     | guinea-pig           | cat          | hamster  | rat | chinchilla         |
| Nationality         | australian  | mexican | thai | spanish   | brazilian | turkish   | french       |
| Game       | bridge   | canasta  | snooker        | poker | backgammon   | billiard    | chess |
| Transport   | van        | taxi       | boat           | train         | subway     | tram       | motorbike    |

