11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
14. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
15. the project-manager is on the far right##1
16. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
17. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
18. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
19. the person drinking tea is the pilot##1
20. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
21. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
22. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the musician##3
23. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
24. the person eating juicerot is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
