.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, tulip, orchid, iris, amaryllis, rose
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, metal, funk, folk, electronic, indie, country
